# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# .dockerignore — applied when running docker build from the monorepo root.
# Excludes files that must never enter the build context:
#   - Large directories that would bloat the context (node_modules, .next, dist)
#   - Secrets (.env files)
#   - Dev tooling and CI artifacts
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Dependencies — reinstalled inside Docker from lockfile
**/node_modules

# Build outputs — rebuilt inside Docker
**/.next
**/dist
**/.turbo

# Environment files — secrets must be injected at runtime via orchestrator env vars,
# never baked into the image
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# Test artifacts
**/coverage
**/__tests__
**/*.spec.ts
**/*.test.ts
**/*.spec.tsx
**/*.test.tsx

# Development tooling
**/.git
**/.github
**/.husky
**/docs
**/*.md
!apps/web/public/**/*.md

# Editor and OS
**/.DS_Store
**/.vscode
**/.idea
**/Thumbs.db

# Docker files themselves (no need to copy into image)
**/Dockerfile
**/.dockerignore
